		<section>
				<h2 id="Section2"><div class="background" style="margin-top: 15px">Career </div></h2>
				<p class="indent">As an experienced advertising professional with a keen eye for detail and self-diagnosed sense of humour, Shelby prides herself on her unique ability to both “break the ice” and simultaneously oversee the intricacies of project management. She brings a flavourful perspective to everything she does, making her a talented user experience specialist, as well as budding writing enthusiast. Her work extends across various media platforms including print, broadcast and web, and her light attitude and collaborative spirit ensures that she can work in a variety of environments with diverse departments and teams. Her love of the design and production of both meaningful and memorable content has allowed her to work on a variety of projects with notable brands the likes of <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u8GMX7wvXrg" target="blank" class="links">Disney</a>, <a href="https://thecommunity.ca/perrier/" target="blank" class="links">Perrier</a>, <a href="https://thecommunity.ca/grey-goose-summer-soiree/" target="blank" class="links">Grey Goose</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cFaE1JFWXTQ" target="blank" class="links">RBC</a>, <a href="https://thecommunity.ca/levis/" target="blank" class="links">Levi's</a>, <a href="https://thecommunity.ca/canadian-tire/" target="blank" class="links">Canadian Tire</a>, <a href="https://www.rexall.ca/inspired-beauty/cosmetics" target="blank" class="links">Rexall</a>, and more.</p>

				<p class="indent">Review Shelby's detailed Resume below.</p>

